ANTE BET
GAME RULES
The player has the option to select the bet multiplier. Depending on the selected bet, the game behaves differently. The possible values are:
Bet multiplier 25x - the chance to win free spins naturally is doubled. More SCATTER symbols are present on the reels. The FREE SPINS PURCHASE FEATURE is disabled.
Bet multiplier 20x - gives the ability to purchase a FREE SPINS ROUND by paying a value equal to 100x total bet.
TUMBLE FEATURE
All wins are added to the player's balance after all of the tumbles resulted from a base spin have been played.

The TUMBLE FEATURE means that after every spin, winning combinations are paid and all winning symbols disappear. The remaining symbols fall to the bottom of the screen and the empty positions are replaced with symbols coming from above.
Tumbling will continue until no more winning combinations appear as a result of a tumble. There's no limit to the number of possible tumbles.
FREE SPINS RULES
The FREE SPINS FEATURE is awarded when 4 or more SCATTER symbols hit anywhere on the screen.
The round starts with 10 free spins.
Whenever 3 or more SCATTER symbols hit during the FREE SPINS ROUND, 5 additional free spins are awarded.
This is the MULTIPLIER symbol.        is present on the reels only during the FREE SPINS ROUND and it stays on the screen until the end of the tumbling sequence.
When the tumbling sequence ends, the values of all        symbols on the screen are added together and the total win of the sequence is multiplied by the final value.
Special reels are in play during the FREE SPINS ROUND.
Whenever a        symbol hits, it takes a random multiplier value of 2x, 3x, 4x, 5x, 6x, 8x, 10x, 12x, 15x, 20x, 25x, 50x or 100x.
GAME RULES
VOLATILITY
Medium volatility games pay out steadily and the range of pays varies from low to very high.
When winning with multiple symbols, all wins are added to the total win.
Free spins win is awarded to the player after the round completes.

Symbols pay anywhere.
All wins are multiplied by base bet.
Free spins total win in the history contains the whole win of the cycle.
All values are expressed as actual wins in coins.
SPACE and ENTER buttons on the keyboard can be used to start and stop the spin.

JACKPOT RULES

There can be up to 4 progressive jackpots available in the game simultaneously. The total amount of each jackpot goes up by a percentage taken from the player's bet. When one of the Jackpots is won by a player, the total resets and begins to build again.
The Jackpots can be won at random at the end of any spin in the base game. Jackpots cannot be won during any of the Free Spins features.

A players chance to win any of the available jackpots is directly related to the bet amount. Higher bets have a higher chance of winning; however, any of the Jackpots can be won at any bet 
amount above the minimum eligible bet.

Jackpot may be temporarily shut down. When the jackpots are shut down, all contributions are stopped and the jackpots are marked as "Jackpot closed". The amount accumulated before shut down remains in the Jackpot and will be available for winning after the jackpots are resumed.
JACKPOT RULES
Due to unavoidable internet lag, the displayed Jackpot amounts may differ from actual values.

If two or more players win the Jackpot at approximately the same time, then all wins are awarded in order, so that each collects the accumulated Jackpot value which exists at the exact moment of their win. The Jackpot is NOT divided equally among several winners.

serializableData._text: Simbol membayar di mana-mana atas skrin. Bilangan simbol yang sama pada skrin pada penghujung putaran akan menentukan nilai kemenangan.
Simbol SCATTER ada pada semua kekili.
Pemain mempunyai pilihan untuk memilih pengganda taruhan. Bergantung pada taruhan yang dipilih, tindak balas permainan adalah berbeza. Nilai yang berkemungkinan ialah:
Pengganda taruhan 25x - peluang untuk memenangi putaran percuma digandakan secara semula jadi. Lebih simbol SCATTER terdapat pada kekili. CIRI PEMBELIAN PUTARAN PERCUMA dinyahdayakan.
Pengganda taruhan 20x - memberi kebolehan untuk membeli PUSINGAN PUTARAN PERCUMA dengan membayar nilai bersamaan 100x jumlah taruhan.
Semua kemenangan ditambah kepada baki pemain selepas semua gulingan yang terhasil daripada putaran asas telah dimainkan.

CIRI GULING bermaksud bahawa selepas setiap putaran, kombinasi kemenangan akan dibayar dan semua simbol kemenangan akan hilang. Simbol yang kekal akan jatuh ke bawah skrin dan posisi kosong digantikan dengan simbol dari atas.
Gulingan akan berterusan sehingga tiada lagi kombinasi kemenangan muncul akibat gulingan. Tiada had untuk bilangan gulingan yang boleh berlaku.
Ciri PUTARAN PERCUMA diberikan apabila 4 atau lebih simbol SCATTER diraih di mana-mana pada skrin.
Apabila 3 atau lebih simbol SCATTER terkena semasa PUSINGAN PUTARAN PERCUMA, 5 putaran percuma tambahan dihadiahkan.
Ini adalah simbol PENGGANDA.          terdapat pada kekili hanya semsasa PUSINGAN PUTARAN PERCUMA dan ia kekal pada skrin sehingga penghujung urutan gulingan.
Apabila urutan gulingan berakhir, nilai semua simbol           pada skrin akan ditambah semua sekali dan jumlah kemenangan urutan digandakan dengan nilai akhir.
Kekili istimewa dimainkan semasa PUSINGAN PUTARAN PERCUMA.
Setiap kali         simbol mencecah, ia memerlukan nilai pengganda rawak 2x, 3x, 4x, 5x, 6x, 8x, 10x, 12x, 15x, 20x, 25x, 50x atau 100x.
Permainan votaliti sederhana membayar secara tetap dan julat bayaran adalah berbeza daripada rendah hingga sangat tinggi
Apabila menang dengan berbilang simbol, semua kemenangan ditambah kepada jumlah kemenangan.
Kemenangan putaran percuma diberikan kepada pemain selepas pusingan selesai.

Semua kemenangan digandakan dengan taruhan asas.
Jumlah kemenangan putaran percuma dalam rekod mengandungi keseluruhan kemenangan kitaran tersebut.
Semua nilai dinyatakan sebagai kemenangan sebenar dalam bentuk syiling
Butang RUANG dan ENTER pada papan kekunci boleh digunakan untuk memulakan dan menghentikan putaran.

Jackpot boleh dimenangi secara rawak pada penghujung mana-mana putaran dalam permainan asas. Jackpot tidak boleh dimenangi semasa mana-mana ciri Putaran Percuma.

Jackpot boleh ditutup secara sementara. Apabila jackpot ditutup, kesemua sumbangan dihentikan dan jackpot ditanda sebagai ""Jackpot ditutup"". Jumlah yang dikumpul sebelum penutupan akan kekal dalam Jackpot dan akan tersedia untuk dimenangi apabila jackpot disambung semula.
Disebabkan oleh lengah internet yang tidak dapat dielakkan, jumlah Jackpot yang dipaparkan mungkin berbeza daripada nilai sebenar.

Jika dua atau lebih pemain memenangi Jackpot pada lebih kurang masa yang sama, maka semua kemenangan dihadiahkan mengikut urutan, agar setiap pemenang mengumpul nilai Jackpot terkumpul yang wujud pada saat mereka menang. Jackpot TIDAK dibahagikan secara sama rata antara beberapa pemenang.
